import React, { useState } from 'react'; import { Eye, AlertTriangle, Clock, TrendingUp, Filter, Download } from 'lucide-react'; const FraudPage = () => { const [selectedAlert, setSelectedAlert] = useState(null); const [filterPriority, setFilterPriority] = useState('all'); const fraudAlerts = [ { id: 'F001', title: 'Multiple Refund Pattern', priority: 'High', riskLevel: 'High', score: 92, description: 'Customer initiated 8 refunds in 24 hours', timestamp: '2 hours ago', category: 'Refund Abuse', customerId: 'C123456789', amount: '$2,347.89', investigationBrief: 'Customer has requested multiple refunds for different products within a 24-hour window, exhibiting classic refund abuse patterns. IP analysis shows consistent location but unusual frequency.', riskIndicators: ['multiple_refunds', 'high_frequency', 'pattern_anomaly', 'velocity_check_fail'], subAgentResults: { 'Payment Analysis': { score: 94, confidence: 'High' }, 'Behavioral Pattern': { score: 91, confidence: 'High' }, 'Account History': { score: 89, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Device Fingerprint': { score: 87, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'F002', title: 'Account Takeover Attempt', priority: 'High', riskLevel: 'High', score: 89, description: 'Login from suspicious IP with different device', timestamp: '3 hours ago', category: 'Account Security', customerId: 'C987654321', amount: '$1,892.45', investigationBrief: 'Unauthorized access attempt detected from a new IP address and device. Login patterns inconsistent with user\'s historical behavior and geographical location.', riskIndicators: ['suspicious_ip', 'new_device', 'geo_anomaly', 'login_pattern_change'], subAgentResults: { 'IP Reputation': { score: 92, confidence: 'High' }, 'Device Analysis': { score: 88, confidence: 'High' }, 'Geolocation Check': { score: 85, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Behavioral Biometrics': { score: 90, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'F003', title: 'Credit Card Testing', priority: 'Medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', score: 76, description: 'Multiple failed payment attempts with different cards', timestamp: '5 hours ago', category: 'Payment Fraud', customerId: 'C456789123', amount: '$156.99', investigationBrief: 'Sequential payment attempts using different credit card numbers detected. Pattern suggests potential card testing or carding activity.', riskIndicators: ['multiple_cards', 'payment_failures', 'card_testing_pattern'], subAgentResults: { 'Card Validation': { score: 78, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Payment Gateway': { score: 74, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Fraud Database': { score: 79, confidence: 'High' } } }, { id: 'F004', title: 'Shipping Address Mismatch', priority: 'Medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', score: 68, description: 'Billing and shipping addresses in different countries', timestamp: '6 hours ago', category: 'Address Verification', customerId: 'C789123456', amount: '$789.33', investigationBrief: 'Significant geographical discrepancy between billing and shipping addresses raises concerns about payment method legitimacy.', riskIndicators: ['address_mismatch', 'country_difference', 'shipping_risk'], subAgentResults: { 'Address Verification': { score: 70, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Geolocation Analysis': { score: 66, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Shipping Intelligence': { score: 69, confidence: 'Low' } } }, { id: 'F005', title: 'Velocity Check Failure', priority: 'Low', riskLevel: 'Low', score: 54, description: 'Unusual purchase frequency detected', timestamp: '8 hours ago', category: 'Behavioral', customerId: 'C321654987', amount: '$234.56', investigationBrief: 'Purchase frequency has increased beyond normal parameters for this customer profile, warranting monitoring.', riskIndicators: ['velocity_anomaly', 'frequency_increase'], subAgentResults: { 'Transaction Velocity': { score: 56, confidence: 'Low' }, 'Customer Profile': { score: 52, confidence: 'Medium' } } }, { id: 'F006', title: 'Duplicate Transaction Pattern', priority: 'Medium', riskLevel: 'Medium', score: 71, description: 'Same items purchased multiple times rapidly', timestamp: '12 hours ago', category: 'Transaction Pattern', customerId: 'C654987321', amount: '$445.67', investigationBrief: 'Customer has made identical purchases in rapid succession, which may indicate automated purchasing or account compromise.', riskIndicators: ['duplicate_transactions', 'rapid_succession', 'automation_suspected'], subAgentResults: { 'Transaction Analysis': { score: 73, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Pattern Recognition': { score: 69, confidence: 'Medium' }, 'Automation Detection': { score: 75, confidence: 'High' } } } ]; const handleAction = (id, action) => { console.log(`Action taken on ${id}: ${action}`); // Add actual implementation here }; const filteredAlerts = filterPriority === 'all' ? fraudAlerts : fraudAlerts.filter(alert => alert.priority === filterPriority); const getPriorityColor = (priority) => { switch (priority) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600 text-white'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500 text-black'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500 text-white'; default: return 'bg-neutral-600 text-white'; } }; const getScoreColor = (score) => { if (score >= 80) return 'text-red-400'; if (score >= 60) return 'text-yellow-400'; return 'text-green-400'; }; const stats = { totalAlerts: fraudAlerts.length, highPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'High').length, mediumPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'Medium').length, lowPriority: fraudAlerts.filter(a => a.priority === 'Low').length, totalAmount: fraudAlerts.reduce((sum, alert) => sum + parseFloat(alert.amount.replace('$', '').replace(',', '')), 0) }; return (
{/* Header Section */}

Fraud Detection

Real-time fraud monitoring and alert management

{/* Stats Cards */}

High Priority

{stats.highPriority}

Medium Priority

{stats.mediumPriority}

Low Priority

{stats.lowPriority}

Total Value

${stats.totalAmount.toLocaleString()}

{/* Alerts Grid */}
{filteredAlerts.map((alert) => (
setSelectedAlert(alert)} className="cursor-pointer bg-neutral-700 rounded-lg p-5 border border-neutral-600 hover:border-neutral-400 hover:bg-neutral-600 transition" >
{alert.id} {alert.priority}

{alert.title}

{alert.description}

Customer ID: {alert.customerId}
Amount: {alert.amount}
Category: {alert.category}
{alert.timestamp}
Risk Score: {alert.score}%
))}
); }; const InvestigationPanel = ({ selectedAlert, handleAction }) => { const getRiskColor = (riskLevel) => { switch (riskLevel) { case 'High': return 'bg-red-600/90 text-white border-red-400'; case 'Medium': return 'bg-yellow-500/90 text-black border-yellow-400'; case 'Low': return 'bg-green-500/90 text-white border-green-400'; default: return 'bg-neutral-700 text-white border-neutral-600'; } }; return (

Investigation Details

{selectedAlert ? (

{selectedAlert.title}

{selectedAlert.riskLevel} Risk

{selectedAlert.description}

Investigation Brief

{selectedAlert.investigationBrief}

Risk Indicators

{selectedAlert.riskIndicators && selectedAlert.riskIndicators.map((indicator, index) => ( {indicator.replace('_', ' ').toUpperCase()} ))}

Sub-Agent Analysis

{selectedAlert.subAgentResults && Object.entries(selectedAlert.subAgentResults).map(([agent, result]) => (
{agent.replace(/([A-Z])/g, ' $1').trim()}
{result.score}%
{result.confidence} Confidence
))}
) : (

No Alert Selected

Select an alert from the dashboard to view investigation details

)}
); }; export default FraudPage;
